Source: stellar-horizon
Section: web
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Package Maintainer <packages@stellar.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>=9), dh-systemd (>=1.5)
Standards-Version: 3.9.6
Homepage: https://www.stellar.org/

Package: stellar-horizon
Architecture: any
Depends: postgresql-client, postgresql-client-common
Recommends: stellar-horizon-utils
Description: Horizon is the client facing API server for the Stellar ecosystem.
 It acts as the interface between stellar-core and applications that want to access the Stellar network.
 It allows you to submit transactions to the network, check the status of accounts, subscribe to event streams, etc.
